Installation
============

    git clone http://github.com/Cassus/CCE-web.git
    cd CCE-web
    git submodule update --init --recursive
    cp config/autoconfig_template.yml config/autoconfig.yml
    #create database user and edit config/autoconfig.yml
    $EDITOR config/autoconfig.yml
    mkdir log cache
    ./symfony project:autoconfig config/autoconfig.yml
    ./symfony project:permissions
    ./symfony doctrine:build --db --and-migrate --and-load

Development
===========

Regenerate base model and DB migrations
---------------------------------------

    rm -r lib/migration/doctrine/ ; \
    symfony cc &&
    symfony doctrine:build --all-classes &&
    symfony doctrine:generate-migrations-models &&
    symfony doctrine:build --db --and-migrate --and-load --no-confirmation
